{"tid":410854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（警惕台獨）庫德族獨立公投在聯合國壓力下宣布取消","createTime":"2017-09-23T09:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T11:17:10.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0371c1b23c8b60662d5fdb19a66a8924583ff3","tid":410854,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"正在紐約參加聯合國大會的伊拉克、土耳其及伊朗外長發表聯合聲明，要求伊拉克庫爾德人自治區，取消獨立公投。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其及伊朗擔心，伊拉克庫爾德人尋求獨立，會為本國境內的庫爾德人，帶來示範作用，危害國家安全和領土完整，因此一直強烈反對公投。<br />\n<br />\n庫爾德人在打擊極端組織的過程中，逐漸成為不可忽視的力量，國際社會憂慮公投結果，會否影響針對極端組織的行動、引發地區衝突或更大規模連鎖反應。伊拉克庫爾德人自治區領導層，近日面對周邊國家及美國的壓力，已改口稱不拒絕尋求公投以外的替代方案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E4%BC%8A%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E4%BF%83%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E5%BA%AB%E7%88%BE%E5%BE%B7%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E5%8D%80%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95-084922105.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%2580%25B3%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%258A%2595-084922105.html&d=fjFj6EJ132DHupDyyeTtef%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e11bf953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E4%BC%8A%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E4%BF%83%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E5%BA%AB%E7%88%BE%E5%BE%B7%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E5%8D%80%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95-084922105.html</a><br />\n聯合國真係最大既維穩力量"},{"pid":"f2ea853bb472a4be8a57ea41af281c61dc3f3418","tid":410854,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"標題黨五毛注意"},{"pid":"91f899ba26b503c03ef9cd9ac154fa308604